name: Cardiology Clinic
description: Cardiology clinics specialize in diagnosing and treating heart diseases and related healthcare services. They offer a wide range of services, including cardiac screenings, EKGs, and heart surgery consultations.

name: Orthopedic Center
description: Orthopedic centers focus on musculoskeletal healthcare, including bone and joint health. They provide services such as orthopedic surgeries, joint replacements, and sports injury treatments.

name: Mental Health Clinic
description: Mental health clinics offer comprehensive mental healthcare services. They provide therapy, counseling, and psychiatric consultations to address various mental health conditions.

name: Women's Health Center
description: Women's health centers specialize in women's healthcare needs. They offer services like prenatal care, gynecology, and reproductive healthcare.

name: Pediatric Hospital
description: Pediatric hospitals focus on healthcare for children. They provide pediatric surgeries, vaccinations, and specialized care for infants and young patients.

name: Cancer Treatment Center
description: Cancer treatment centers specialize in oncology and cancer care. They offer treatments such as chemotherapy, radiation therapy, and cancer screenings.

name: Dental Clinic
description: Dental clinics provide oral healthcare services. They offer dental check-ups, teeth cleanings, and various dental procedures to maintain oral health.

name: Urgent Care Center
description: Urgent care centers offer immediate healthcare for non-life-threatening conditions. They provide quick medical attention for various health issues.

name: Physical Therapy Clinic
description: Physical therapy clinics focus on rehabilitation and physical health. They offer services like rehabilitation exercises and injury recovery.

name: Geriatric Care Facility
description: Geriatric care facilities cater to the healthcare needs of elderly individuals. They provide specialized care for aging patients and offer services such as assisted living and memory care.
